## colors

# class                 border  backgr. text    indic.  child_border
client.focused          #000000 #000000 #FFFFFF #FDF6E3
client.focused_inactive #000000 #000000 #A0A0A0 #454948
client.unfocused        #000000 #000000 #A0A0A0 #454948
